{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/2019/09/piano-solo-time-to-say-goodbye/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"b66acdb4-7ce4-507c-a82a-2afeaf37bc40","html":"<!-- endExcerpt -->\n<p><div class=\"gatsby-resp-iframe-wrapper\" style=\"padding-bottom: 56.49999999999999%; position: relative; height: 0; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem\" > <div class=\"embedVideo-container\"> <iframe title=\"\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/q0chGWzSBrU?rel=0\" class=\"embedVideo-iframe\" style=\"border:0; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; \" loading=\"eager\" allowfullscreen=\"\" sandbox=\"allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-popups\"></iframe> </div> </div></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://v.qq.com/x/page/l3005rsphgm.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">在腾讯视频上</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"背景\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF\" aria-label=\"背景 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>背景</h2>\n<p>六年前，当我离开三峡晚报社，坐上去武汉的火车时，新闻理想早已崩溃。</p>\n<p>虽然放弃了一些坚持，开始对一些事情变得无所谓，但是当火车缓慢启动，远处三峡物流园的字缓慢移近然后消失在身后时，想着她在我镜头记录下，从一片荒芜到车水马龙，想着宜昌的大街小巷和人情冷暖，不免有一些不舍之情。</p>\n<p>戴上耳机放了这首 Time To Say Goodbye，我知道我会记得这一刻，记得那些坚持。</p>\n<p>弹这首曲子送给自己，并<strong>敬有坚持的人</strong>！</p>\n<h2 id=\"piano-sheet\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#piano-sheet\" aria-label=\"piano sheet permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Piano Sheet</h2>\n<p>作曲：Francesco Sartori</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://musescore.com/user/125146/scores/906416\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Download</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"练习\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%BB%83%E4%B9%A0\" aria-label=\"练习 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>练习</h2>\n<p>这是去年学的一首曲子，时隔一年疏于练习反而不如以前弹得好。反复录制都无法完整无错弹奏，最后只好剪切处理。我的基本功还远不能掌握这样的曲子，还是要多练基础。</p>\n<h2 id=\"指法键盘顶视图\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%8C%87%E6%B3%95%E9%94%AE%E7%9B%98%E9%A1%B6%E8%A7%86%E5%9B%BE\" aria-label=\"指法键盘顶视图 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>指法键盘顶视图</h2>\n<p><div class=\"ga